## Validation Checklist

Before using these personas:

- [ ] Each persona represents a **distinct user type** with unique goals
- [ ] Personas are based on **real user research** (interviews, surveys, existing data)
- [ ] **Primary persona** is clearly identified (80% of user stories will serve them)
- [ ] Pain points are **specific and measurable**, not vague ("slow" → "checkout takes >3 min")
- [ ] Demographics are **relevant** to system design (don't include irrelevant details)
- [ ] Anti-personas help **prevent scope creep**

